{"tid":2310112,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［長文］留 喺 度 抗 爭 嘅 人 其 實 好 撚 戇 鳩 ，係 必 定 後 悔 ～","createTime":"2020-12-03T04:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T16:32:57.000Z","uid":219007,"like":23,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f0f07d09da158841581a2055833964fdcf7d7f5c","tid":2310112,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:36:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"small\">我知道我講嘅說話好多人都唔啱聽，但係現實說話就係咁難聽，而現實就必須要認清，唔能夠逃避，否則只係會喺自己空間，同林鄭係冇分別。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有唔少人喺度期望緊疫情完咗之後街頭抗爭重現嘅畫面，其實疫情完咗反而係移民潮多於一切。 <span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">香港根本就冇得你抗爭，留得喺度嘅就為兩餐投誠做一件仆街，否則你就離開。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人從來都係從功能性思考角度處事，做嘢講求效率為優先。<span class=\"red\">當佢哋定立左目標之後，佢哋就會尋找一個成本最低嘅方法去達成目標</span>，即係依家啲人成日講嘅「<strong>性價比</strong>」。 呢個就係香港嘅核心價值，<strong><em><span class=\"red\">功利主義</span></em></strong>。 由始至終都沒有變過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">香港人從來都冇乜大志，求嘅嘢非常卑微，只係「安居樂業」</span>。 雖然係非常卑微，但係香港已經俾唔到佢。 依家喺香港人手中有兩種選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><strong>A. 移民外地 </strong></span><br />\n<strong>成本</strong>：一舊錢 + 5-6年光陰 。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>效益</strong>：9成成功換來安穩生活。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"blue\">B. 留喺香港（首先要爭取民主）</span></strong> <br />\n<strong>成本</strong>：輕則失去自由（非法集結都要坐六個月監、掟雞蛋坐2x個月） 及在港工作前途，重則終身殘廢/失去性命，仲要係一代人又一代人付出血汗性命前途。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>效益</strong>：肯定短期之內（5-6年）不成功，長遠完全未知，可能需要20-30年時間甚至永遠失敗。<br />\n<br />\n以香港人一貫嘅衡量處事方式，答案已經非常明顯。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺宜家呢個形勢，香港人一早已經有咗選擇，<span class=\"red\">呢個係香港最殘酷嘅現實，只係手足太後生未明白</span>。<br />\n<br />\n手足成日話而家靜哂會令人忘記所以一定要繼續出嚟，<span class=\"red\">其實香港人從來冇忘記過警暴，只不過係無能為力，橫掂日子都要過倒不如過得開心啲咁解</span>。 但亦都唔好覺得疫情之後香港人會再次出嚟，因為走嘅人肯定遠比你想像中更多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時候留喺度抗爭嘅人因為冇咗一班和理非移左民嘅支持，客觀形勢就會更加危險，一係就俾人拉，一係就慢慢磨蝕為求生存接受現實投誠。當然你亦都可以講移左民繼續支持香港手足，但現實咁去睇當時間耐左，<span class=\"red\">走咗嘅人自然就會慢慢關心少咗香港，多咗時間投放喺自己生活，呢樣野亦都係無得批評同避免。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以話留喺度抗爭嘅人幾十年之後就會後悔</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「<strong>出到去就可以有新生活，咁仲使鬼留喺度爭取咩</strong>」其實已經反映香港人嘅核心價值，「<strong>醒目仔</strong>」、「<strong>精甩尾</strong>」同「<strong>搵着數</strong>」一早已經成為香港人嘅標籤。 當然我係十分尊敬話要留喺度抗爭嘅人，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">但如果從功利角度去睇，其實好撚戇鳩</span></span></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港要死可以由得佢，但係<span class=\"red\">只要每個人都顧掂自己，好自然就會救到晒所有人</span>。 所以大家必須要認清現實，係時候對自己好啲。 <br />\n<br />\n我對呢度仲有一絲嘅樂觀係源於侵，如果都失敗埋，一日中國存在，呢到都唔會有希望。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><ins>係香港人既，齊上齊落，一齊走啦</ins></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e37ad3432cc2d7e0db7e4dc205444b751b7ac18","tid":2310112,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:38:50.000Z","msg":"鍾意你嘅分析<br />\n<br />\n香港人包括我自己都係咁搵到個目標一定係搵最低成本嘅方法去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以唔難解釋點解咁多閪老闆"},{"pid":"168da558a95c4c1c338521a0891dec015345e8e1","tid":2310112,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352102b8e5e1b494c72266ea8de60268474d8c1c","tid":2310112,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:41:28.000Z","msg":"所以有能力既多數留低繼續搵錢<br />\n或者繼續食下女，好似孔德賢咁"},{"pid":"534dabd09cfdeb736bba2f84feb46088ac93d2b4","tid":2310112,"uid":229977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"352102b8e5e1b494c72266ea8de60268474d8c1c","tid":2310112,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:41:28.000Z","msg":"所以有能力既多數留低繼續搵錢<br />\n或者繼續食下女，好似孔德賢咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"多數有外國國籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846b42e662f3f663a67bdff553730a2113d06bfc","tid":2310112,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60934b28656c713d7c4dff96d10fb3613eb977d1","tid":2310112,"uid":148883,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:49:37.000Z","msg":"一日唔支爆 真係諗唔到可以點反cup <br />\n依家仲要china joe當選 i see no hope<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90c14cb2c611d518987cca6ee4a42000c53c9ec9","tid":2310112,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa9462b62d574b203c8949859c42faf892e91e0","tid":2310112,"uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:54:47.000Z","msg":"話要移民嗰d又係哂鳩氣<br />\n激嬲完共產黨，原來自己又淆底到要走佬<br />\n咁你呢年幾兩年究竟響到做乜鳩啫"},{"pid":"69935385d474d1e1995b60e68b0650d395493832","tid":2310112,"uid":15010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fa9462b62d574b203c8949859c42faf892e91e0","tid":2310112,"uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:54:47.000Z","msg":"話要移民嗰d又係哂鳩氣<br />\n激嬲完共產黨，原來自己又淆底到要走佬<br />\n咁你呢年幾兩年究竟響到做乜鳩啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:57:06.000Z","msg":"即刻有隻五毛入左黎"},{"pid":"e7d69441b54a75bde6f9ab85cda33dd4cf7eb32d","tid":2310112,"uid":271485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"唔係喎<br />\n當年青政熱狗都話入政府攞資源抗爭喎<br />\n而家每日都有人用呢個理由去考公務員喎<br />\n又唔係嗱？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b098de92da5c2d9bccf284ca67ff4dc4dd151f","tid":2310112,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eefd31b54e07bad5e8e639e33dfaf0a45f8739b","tid":2310112,"uid":168492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:12:52.000Z","msg":"最起碼我唔駛再俾稅俾正苦去買子彈先<br />\n維穩都要錢架"},{"pid":"09a6646785f87f02d68a2d31fe41522ef70a9110","tid":2310112,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497ae8bc06d19f5df6a6f47d69ce841a86d13983","tid":2310112,"uid":59297,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:14:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">大家自己起底，條友出po有晒格式，係咩人自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//香港根本就冇得你抗爭，留得喺度嘅就為兩餐投誠做一件仆街，否則你就離開。//<br />\n<br />\n講到尾你都係想潑冷水，笑鳩啲堅持嘅人，逼鳩人行你嗰套做港豬安穩生活，仲擺出副大人教細路嘅姿態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留低堅持抗爭=仆街<br />\n違背良心走佬放棄=醒目仔<br />\n<br />\n你講嘅嘢同藍絲有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69789975baa28285a3d5977adfe63a9a34cc103e","tid":2310112,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fa9462b62d574b203c8949859c42faf892e91e0","tid":2310112,"uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:54:47.000Z","msg":"話要移民嗰d又係哂鳩氣<br />\n激嬲完共產黨，原來自己又淆底到要走佬<br />\n咁你呢年幾兩年究竟響到做乜鳩啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"跟住呢隻著名五毛就出嚟扯貓尾引戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6fa6bf9420340bc098972fa2c1acc6d0f5e5c0","tid":2310112,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7d69441b54a75bde6f9ab85cda33dd4cf7eb32d","tid":2310112,"uid":271485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"唔係喎<br />\n當年青政熱狗都話入政府攞資源抗爭喎<br />\n而家每日都有人用呢個理由去考公務員喎<br />\n又唔係嗱？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:16:05.000Z","msg":"議會都完撚咗，又一隻五毛入嚟搵稻草人打，關熱狗青政撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0779703c58bdc8f970f25f645a3c852d310a4445","tid":2310112,"uid":89641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:16:34.000Z","msg":"完全同意, 我同女朋友都PLAN好左儲錢移民, 交稅都要交比一個值得交既政府。"},{"pid":"b204719476507fbcda9077a7da9b32ef2cb1c1c3","tid":2310112,"uid":245523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:18:22.000Z","msg":"性價比呢個字講得好啱<br />\n當初我衡量過 為信念坐非法集結坐返一年半載 我覺得ok<br />\n但要付出更多代價嘅話 我就會卻步 <br />\n球證球員觀眾連清潔姐姐都係對家嘅人 要個公正判決只能求自己好彩唔會遇到釘官<br />\n有個成語叫「投石問路」 遇到自己唔熟悉嘅道路 dum幾舊石去試吓情況 而依家已經有好多舊不幸嘅石頭指出呢條路係死路"},{"pid":"d291fea58022140728c7895f999f194da5907f23","tid":2310112,"uid":156254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"香港己經破局<br />\n一係移民, 一係做順民"},{"pid":"8082b4999dc989b6e63a718823c50ed2acb4463b","tid":2310112,"uid":80178,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7fa9462b62d574b203c8949859c42faf892e91e0","tid":2310112,"uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:54:47.000Z","msg":"話要移民嗰d又係哂鳩氣<br />\n激嬲完共產黨，原來自己又淆底到要走佬<br />\n咁你呢年幾兩年究竟響到做乜鳩啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:19:20.000Z","msg":"班人駁唔到就話你5毛, pr架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以從來唔覺得依班小學雞會贏<br />\n就算贏左都會差過依家"},{"pid":"04f6864707d7f49a5f1f16ffe7f62eb87c81ff66","tid":2310112,"uid":271485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d6fa6bf9420340bc098972fa2c1acc6d0f5e5c0","tid":2310112,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7d69441b54a75bde6f9ab85cda33dd4cf7eb32d","tid":2310112,"uid":271485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"唔係喎<br />\n當年青政熱狗都話入政府攞資源抗爭喎<br />\n而家每日都有人用呢個理由去考公務員喎<br />\n又唔係嗱？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:16:05.000Z","msg":"議會都完撚咗，又一隻五毛入嚟搵稻草人打，關熱狗青政撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:27:31.000Z","msg":"泰博仲响度喎，每日都有人考公務員喎。"},{"pid":"d13a65a07b65f04fec4c1453d13aaf870a828268","tid":2310112,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T06:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc41b9ce82be27824b8a6d88fe324e24c27bc79","tid":2310112,"uid":114193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"497ae8bc06d19f5df6a6f47d69ce841a86d13983","tid":2310112,"uid":59297,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:14:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">大家自己起底，條友出po有晒格式，係咩人自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//香港根本就冇得你抗爭，留得喺度嘅就為兩餐投誠做一件仆街，否則你就離開。//<br />\n<br />\n講到尾你都係想潑冷水，笑鳩啲堅持嘅人，逼鳩人行你嗰套做港豬安穩生活，仲擺出副大人教細路嘅姿態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留低堅持抗爭=仆街<br />\n違背良心走佬放棄=醒目仔<br />\n<br />\n你講嘅嘢同藍絲有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T16:32:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2306019/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2306019/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2300489/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2300489/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2276817/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2184746/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2057472/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2057472/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2059235/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2059235/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2073990/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2046361/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1850160/page/1</a><br />\n年幾以來始終如一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}